trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Ger stöd för designtid för <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: CatalogZoneDesigner provides design-time rendering of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> controls.
trans-unit.target: CatalogZoneDesigner ger designläge återgivningen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>

trans-unit.source: It includes support for editable designer regions, templates, and auto-formats to allow a page developer to easily alter the appearance of the control.
trans-unit.target: Det innehåller stöd för redigerbara designer områden, mallar och automatisk-format för att tillåta en sida-utvecklare att enkelt ändra utseendet på kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The public <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collections provide quick formatting options for the page developer and can be safely overridden to change the default appearance of a custom control.
trans-unit.target: Offentligt <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>samlingar ger snabb formateringsalternativ för sidan utvecklare och på ett säkert sätt kan åsidosättas om du vill ändra standardutseendet för en anpassad kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner"></xref> class
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner"> </xref> klass

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of predefined automatic formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box for the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar mängden fördefinierade automatisk formatering scheman ska visas i den **automatisk formatering** dialogrutan för den associerade kontrollen i designläge.

trans-unit.source: The AutoFormats property overrides its base implementation to return a collection that is specific to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Autoformat åsidosätter dess grundläggande implementering för att returnera en samling som är specifik för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>klass.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>

trans-unit.source: A pre-specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> with a default CatalogZone scheme.
trans-unit.target: Före angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> med ett standardschema CatalogZone.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method with a null argument.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den kod som används för att representera kontrollen i designläge genom att anropa den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> metod med en null-argument.

trans-unit.source: A method call to <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> with a null argument as the parameter.
trans-unit.target: Ett metodanrop till <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> med ett null-argument som parameter.

trans-unit.source: Creates an <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> in the designer before generating the design-time HTML of the control.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> i designer innan du genererar designläge HTML för kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref>, if any, associated with the control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref>, om sådant finns, som är associerad med kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> representing the design-time HTML of the control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>representerar designläge HTML för kontrollen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the content for the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar innehållet för den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the persisted form of the designer region's content.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som representerar beständiga form av designer region innehåll.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup to represent an empty control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar koden som representerar en tom kontroll.

trans-unit.source: An empty <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: En tom <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Binder designern till den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Sets the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Anger innehållet i den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the content to go in the specified region.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som representerar innehållet i den angivna regionen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups, each containing one or more template definitions.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling av mallgrupper som innehåller en eller flera Malldefinitioner.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property overrides its base implementation to return a collection that is specific to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups åsidosätter dess grundläggande implementering för att returnera en samling som är specifik för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>klass.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>

trans-unit.source: A pre-specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> with default settings for a CatalogZone environment.
trans-unit.target: Före angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> med standardinställningar för en CatalogZone-miljö.
